				<td colspan="2"><span>Aye, At 61, I would chant kite PoS frogs right by zone in. PULL THEM away from the humanoids, they cast and snare you... dead bard.  The trees and wandering animals don't aggro you.
<br />

<br />
Just a word... Long kites. Ok two words.  Took about 15 min to kill a frog (they're all level 61) with all the resists I was getting at 61.  Suggest not trying this til you can land 3 out of 4 songs at least.  
<br />

<br />
Lastly, I totally agree that grouping if you can is much faster exp.
